Pirating can help establish that love relationship with a series also. If I pirate a game that I end up loving, I am more inclined to actually go out an purchase a sequal, or even on occasion such as portal, the actual game, as I like to have an actual hard copy of games I love. 

BTW, I am a NES fan. I have every game on my pc, but I'm still going out buying every nes game I can. Sure it's 20-30 later, but I am actually buying the games. People buy what they like.
